name: プロデューサー
text:
──なぁ、これって
答案用紙じゃないのか？

name: 透
trans: Wait, did I drop them somewhere?

name: プロデューサー
text:
いや、落ちてたわけじゃないけど……
昨日からここに置きっぱなしだったぞ
trans:
No, no, they weren't dropped anywhere...
They've just been left here since yesterday.

text: ちゃんとしまってくれ
trans:
Just remember to
take them away.

I did see your
scores, though.

Want me to
help out, then?
With studying.

name: 透
text:
ごめんごめん
昨日、みんなで見てて
trans:
Sorry, sorry.
I was going over them with everyone yesterday.

name: 透
text: 大丈夫。補講とかないから
trans: I'm fine. No supplementary lessons or anything, after all.

name: プロデューサー
text: （うっ……しまった。別のことを言えば良かったな……）
trans: (Ah... I should've said something else instead...)
